Fetal liver weight

#Fit a linear mixed model adjusting for litter effect

contrasts(fetal$Diet) <- contr.treatment(levels(fetal$Diet), base = 1)

model<-lmer(Liver.g~Diet + (1|MaternalID), data=fetal)
summary(model)
